	Using new (strict) #include directives

	* tredlib/TrEd/Macros.pm:
	New #include <file> and #include "file" directives implemented.
	Now dies on any error during inclusion

	* tredlib/tred.mac: - switched to new strict #include directives

	* tredlib/tred.def: CloneSubtree function added

	* tredlib/Fslib.pm:
	- do not require new-line when parsing header from an array
	- FSFormat::create fixed

	* tredlib/Fs2csts.pm: print <T> if <gram> non-empty

	* tredlib/Csts2fs.pm: using standard copy_tag_to for <D>

	* documentation/manual/tred.xml:
	New #include <file> and #include "file" macro directives documented

	* btred: -D option added to force all debug messages

