2001-11-06  Petr Pajas  <pajas@ufal.ms.mff.cuni.cz>

	* tredlib/Fslib.pm: FSFile->value_line minor changes

	* documentation/Hooks.txt, tred, tredlib/TrEd/Config.pm, tredlib/TrEd/Convert.pm, tredlib/TrEd/TreeView.pm:
	Better foreign charsets support (new config options
	DefaultFileEncoding and DefaultDisplayEncoding added). UTF-8 support
	on input may come soon (hopefully) when TrEd::Convert moves to Text::Iconv.

	Two hooks added: get_value_line_hook, get_nodelist_hook.

