2001-10-29  Petr Pajas  <pajas@ufal.ms.mff.cuni.cz>

	* tredlib/contrib/winsetup.sh: LibXML installation added

	* tredlib/contrib/ValLex/Data.pm, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/LibXMLData.pm, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/chooser.mak:
	minor changes and optimizations

	* tredlib/contrib/tr_common.mak: F8 assigns default attributes

	* tredlib/contrib/ValLex/XML_DOM_Data.pm:
	Initial commit, partially based on the old version of ValLex::Data.

	* tredlib/contrib/ValLex/Chooser.pm, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/Data.pm, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/Editor.pm, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/LibXMLData.pm, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/Widgets.pm, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/chooser.mak, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/chooser.pl, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/libxml-standalone.pl, tredlib/contrib/ValLex/standalone.pl, tredlib/contrib/tr_common.mak:
	Better memory management, several memory leaks avoided (objects
	keeping pointers to real DOM structure are registered as data clients
	and asked to undefine them when data are reloaded). This leads to a
	need to explicitely destroy() (or unregister) DataClient before the last
	reference to it is dropped off.

	* README, tredlib/TrEd/CPConvert.pm: minor changes

