	* tredlib/CSTS_SGML_SP_Backend.pm: gz functionality corrected

	* tredlib/Fs2csts.pm: debug print removed

	* tredlib/csts.doctype:
	initial commit. This file is not maintained here, just a copy is kept.

	* any2any: convertor from any backended format to any other

	* tredlib/contrib/tfa.mak, tredlib/TrEd/Config.pm, tredlib/TrEd/Macros.pm, tredlib/TrEd/Print.pm, tredlib/TrEd/TreeView.pm:
	Minor changes and bug-fixes.

	* tredlib/CSTSBackend.pm, tredlib/CSTS_SGML_SP_Backend.pm, tredlib/Csts2fs.pm, tredlib/Fs2csts.pm, tredlib/Fslib.pm, tredlib/SGMLS.pm, tredlib/csarialm.pfa, tredlib/tredrc:
	New native CSTS backend using SGMLS.pm and nsgmls parser
	Minor changes and bugfixes in Fslib.pm

	* documentation/manual/tred.xml: minor changes

	* documentation/README.SGMLS: initial commit

	* btred, tred, trprint: btred -S option, bug-fixes, minor changes

