	* tredlib/contrib/tredtr.mak:
	submitted changes from Alena, _key macros renamed

	* tred: local copy of File::Spec packages used on systems where
	File::Spec->can(rel2abs) fails. Local copy is stored in tredlib/TFile and
	uses TFile:: namespace.

	* tredlib/TFile/Spec/Functions.pm, tredlib/TFile/Spec/Mac.pm, tredlib/TFile/Spec/OS2.pm, tredlib/TFile/Spec/Unix.pm, tredlib/TFile/Spec/VMS.pm, tredlib/TFile/Spec/Win32.pm, tredlib/TFile/Basename.pm, tredlib/TFile/CheckTree.pm, tredlib/TFile/Compare.pm, tredlib/TFile/Copy.pm, tredlib/TFile/DosGlob.pm, tredlib/TFile/Find.pm, tredlib/TFile/Path.pm, tredlib/TFile/Spec.pm, tredlib/TFile/stat.pm:
	initial commit, these packages replace system File::Spec if it cannot rel2abs
	All the packages use TFile:: namespace.

