2001-02-22  Petr Pajas  <pajas@ufal.ms.mff.cuni.cz>

	* tred:
	Enabled and defined keyboard shortcuts to underlined letters in menu
	Now, if you press Alt+key, TrEd searches for this shortcut in
	user-defined bindigs. On fail, passes the shortcut to Tk, allowing
	menus to popup.

	* tred: list of macros
	some hooks improvements
	user options to suppres messages ({tred,macro,hook,keyboard}Debug -
	the last one was actually present, already)
	position from geometry is saved in the rc-file as well as the dimensions of the canvas

