	Better support for font-settings on non-X11 platforms (see tredrc)
	Print under-text color bug fixed
	Reload config function added (of course not all options may take effect)

	* tred, btred: Minor bug in libDir search fixed

	* tred:
	PsFontFile config option - file may be given w-o path to make tred
	search for it in libDir

	* tredlib/tredrc: Several new fields commented templates added

	* btred: new libDir handling updated from Tred

	* tredlib/Cprecode.pm, tredlib/Fslib.pm, tredlib/right.xpm, tredlib/tred.def, tredlib/tred.mac, tredlib/tred.xpm, tredlib/tred2.xpm, examples/foreachnode.pl, examples/foreachtree.pl, examples/fortrees.pl, examples/fsdiff.pl, README, btred:
	Minor changes.

	* tred: * Colors for highlited attributes
	* Slightly improved search for libDir
	* Several config options added (colors etc.)
	* Single tree-print bug fixed
	* Macro evaluation memory leak fixed
	* Tree operation functions added (also to menu)
	* Charset conversion for better support on M$ platforms added

